  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">An Explanation of Cookies Cookies are alphanumeric identifiers that are placed by us on your computer s storage system through your web browser to enable our systems to recognize your browser when you make future visits to our Websites and to store certain information such as items placed in your shopping cart between visits</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

